**Capital Raising Announcement (Appendix 2A - Application for Quotation)**  

- **Structure**: Share Purchase Plan (SPP)  
- **Total Capital Raised (SPP)**: AUD 282,000 (upsized from AUD 250,000 due to demand)  
- **Placement Tranche Pending**: 7.18 million shares to directors/related parties (subject to shareholder approval under ASX Listing Rule 10.11)  
- **Issue Price**: AUD 0.05 per share  
- **Quotation Date**: 27 June 2025 (for 5.64 million SPP shares)  
- **Post-Issue Issued Capital**: 365.3 million ordinary shares (quoted) + unquoted options/rights (details in Part 4.2).  

**Key Detail**: SPP oversubscribed; director-related placement pending approval. No other material dates or pricing changes noted.
